HelpLinks: React.FC<HelpLinksProps> = ...
  • Defined in packages/components-next/src/HelpLinks/index.tsx:45

Renders a HelpLinks component. This component is used to create Stack Overflow and Symphony help links.

example

  stackoverflowUrl="https://jpmc.stackenterprise.co/questions/tagged/3273"
  symphonyUrl="symphony://?streamId=RRiNRrpFp3KRM4zfUAlZ1n___o2Kys6zdA&streamType=chatroom"
/>
